Interface MHUSentence

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Sentence

    public interface MHUSentence
extends Sentence

    Relative and absolute humidity with dew point.

    Notice: not recommended as of Oct 2008, should use XDR instead.

    Author:
    Kimmo Tuukkanen
